                <p>Want some additional help getting started? Need advice on how to talk to parents about brightwheel? We’re here to help. We’ve gathered handy guides, how-to videos, sample emails, and more.</p>
                <%= link_to 'Visit our Teacher Resources Page', '#', :class => 'btn btn-default' %>
              </div>
            </div>

